Goal 1: Give the user the correct web address 
Goal 2: Give a login Id and password for each user
Goal 3: Once the user is logged in ask them to select the city
Goal 4: Show the user the available concerts in that city
Goal 5: Once the user selects the concert show the available tickets to the user
Goal 6: Once the ticket is selected take them to the payment portal
Goal 7: Once the payment is done send them a confirmation mail
